title: Ep 263 - Gogi Sodhi Is Angry.
shortDesc: While the other kids from the Tappu Sena are at the ad shoot, Gogi is angry and throwing tantrums at his parents for not being selected. His parents Mr. and Mrs. Roshan are trying their best to convince him. What will happen next? Watch to find out.

title: Ep 264 - Daya Is Excited For Tappu.
shortDesc: Daya is very excited about her son's ad coming on TV. She is calling everyone she knows and informing them to watch the ad without fail. Later, she comes up with a brilliant plan to watch the ad together with the society members.

title: Ep 265 - Lights, Camera, Power Off!
shortDesc: Gokuldham society gathers to watch the ad in which their children have acted. But, just before the ad gets telecasted, the power goes off at Gokuldham society. How will the society members watch the ad now?

title: Ep 266 - Tappu Sena Is Famous!
shortDesc: After Tappu Sena played in an advertisement, people started recognizing them and taking autographs from them. Gogi feels bad for not being a part of this and threatens to run away if he doesn't become famous.

title: Ep 267 - Tappu Has A Plan To Make Gogi Special
shortDesc: Gogi forces Tappu to make him famous. Tappu soon comes up with a mysterious, secret plan to make Gogi appear on Tv but, clearly warns Tappu Sena to not tell this to anyone. Will Gogi become famous? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 268 - Gogi Goes Missing
shortDesc: Tappu Sena comes up with a plan to hide Gogi and spread a fake news that he's missing. How will this plan work? Will Tappu Sena get into trouble? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 269 - Mr. And Mrs. Sodhi Are Worried
shortDesc: Now that Tappu Sena has established that Gogi is missing, the parents are freaking out. They look for Gogi in and around the society but, fail to find him. Where will they find Gogi?

title: Ep 270 - Gokuldham Society Visit The Police Station
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham Society decide to report a complaint to the police. Meanwhile, the Tappu Sena is waiting for Gogi's missing case to telecast on Tv.

title: Ep 271 - Tappu Sena In Trouble
shortDesc: Seeing Gogi missing from the flat Tappu Sena had hidden him in, they are petrified. Muddled, they go to Champaklal for help. Will Gogi be found? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 272 - The Police Create A Fuss
shortDesc: When the police learn that Gogi has been found within the society, they are furious. They later explain that it was their duty to inform the police about Gogi being found. Gogi is extremely happy as he gets selected to act in an advertisement.

title: Ep 273 - Taarak Is Sick Of Diet Food
shortDesc: Anjali again presents a plate of freshly cut salad in front of Taarak and refuses when he asks her to add something to it for it to not taste bland. She later asks Taarak to join a gym but he denies.

title: Ep 274 - Stubborn Chmapaklal
shortDesc: While Jethalal and Bhide argue with each other, Champaklal carries the LPG cylinder himself and leaves for his house. Seeing this, Jethalal runs behind him and takes the cylinder from him. What happens next will leave you laughing.

title: Ep 275 - Babita Decides To Join A Club
shortDesc: Jethalal finds that a rat has nibbled onto his shoes. Left without any options, he has to go out wearing Daya's footwear. Later, Babita gets an offer to become a swimming instructor at a club.

title: Ep 276 - Babita Influences The Ladies To Take Swimming Classes
shortDesc: Babita decides to be a swimming coach at the club. She calls the ladies to join the club and learn swimming from her. Will the ladies join the swimming class?

title: Ep 277 - Jethalal Also Wants To Learn Swimming
shortDesc: After learning that the ladies are planning to take swimming classes, Jethalal is eager to learn swimming from Babita. He seeks help from Taarak. Will Taarak help his friend out?
